{"id": 2004, "genre": 1000, "title": "实体店购物的时候，哪些细节会让你觉得“哎哟，不错哦”？", "description": "都在说“打造好的购物体验”，到底哪些体验是好的？欢迎在评论区补充！（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 19661, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201711101439280oPe4BlzEp1XUdsu.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-12T17:00:23Z", "questions": [{"id": 3273, "title": "实体店购物的时候，哪些细节会让你觉得“哎哟，不错哦”？", "content": "实体店购物的时候，哪些细节会让你觉得“哎哟，不错哦”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 247457, "content": "衣服店附带咖啡厅，至少一小块能坐着休息吃吃喝喝的地方", "image": "img/option/option/20171112082648JE0Xa2QTIvFKVCRW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247459, "content": "家居店直接做成样板间的样子，方便参考着配套买", "image": "img/option/option/20171112090239Si9oRaUzFxnDC1ed.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247460, "content": "购物中心甚至品牌店内部辟出地方做展览，没什么要买的时候也能去逛逛", "image": "img/option/option/20171112090314BiKVGCjv4mQkRIf5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247461, "content": "买完东西之后店家可以直接帮忙发快递", "image": "img/option/option/20171112090401dvQ02SUMjmaOnH6I.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247464, "content": "推出一些便利功能，代收快递、引入共享充电宝雨伞什么的", "image": "img/option/option/20171112090501AuMk8fIB4qCWvXgP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247467, "content": "走在电子化世代前列，订座点菜付款到开发票都能用手机完成", "image": "img/option/option/20171112090543z4Gknd0tNvqafixs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247641, "content": "导购只在我有问题叫 ta 的时候出现，或者压根不需要导购", "image": "img/option/option/20171112090653AwXte3aRIGTvSZoQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247643, "content": "有详细的室内地图或导航 App，让我迅速找到想要的商品", "image": "img/option/option/20171112090808ipYOXhl0Logv3c9z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 247644, "content": "餐厅承诺上菜时间，并用沙漏、计时器“自我监督”", "image": "img/option/option/20171112091445SUIPLDe8czbZF9lE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}